    IsBoundToBuffer
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>IsBoundToBuffer</TypeRef> method reports whether this attribute has already been bound to a buffer.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[bool IsBoundToBuffer() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        True if this attribute has been bound to a buffer, false otherwise.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
